### ============================================
### API DE AUTENTICACIÓN (LOGIN)
### ============================================

### 1. Login - Usuario Admin
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 2. Login - Usuario Cliente
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "cliente1",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 3. Login - Credenciales incorrectas
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### 4. Registro de nuevo usuario
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/registro
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "nuevocliente",
  "password": "123456",
  "nombre": "Pedro Nuevo",
  "email": "pedro@example.com",
  "telefono": "555-9999"
}

### 5. Verificar si un usuario existe
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/verificar/cliente1

### ============================================
### API DE CONSULTA DE TABLAS - USUARIOS
### ============================================

### 6. Obtener todos los usuarios
GET http://localhost:8080/api/usuarios

### 7. Obtener usuario por ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/usuarios/1

### 8. Actualizar usuario
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/usuarios/3
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Juan Pérez Actualizado",
  "email": "juan.nuevo@example.com",
  "telefono": "555-1234"
}

### 9. Cambiar contraseña
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/usuarios/3/password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "passwordActual": "123456",
  "passwordNueva": "nuevapass123"
}

### 10. Desactivar usuario
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/usuarios/5/desactivar

### 11. Eliminar usuario
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/usuarios/5

### ============================================
### API DE CONSULTA DE TABLAS - RESTAURANTES
